<p><strong>Available Patron Themes:</strong> <Link to="/patron/moon">Moon</Link>, <Link to="/patron/plague">Plague</Link>, <Link to="/patron/shadow">Shadow</Link>, <Link to="/patron/vengeance">Vengeance</Link></p>
